      "side": 1,
      "message": "I think the biggest issue here is the FreeType side not applying the FT_Face\u0027s size or transform to the values, leaving them in em space. The issue being that this *is* being applied by FreeType to the outlines being generated. FreeType is the only one that can keep these transformations consistent. Also, letting FreeType handle the scaling means allowing it to do whatever magic it wants in the scaling (like autohinting points if it feels like it).",
      "revId": "85b37637cbc8e77babcc641bad511013f1b608ea",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02"
    },
