      "writtenOn": "2021-01-14T19:11:09Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "This unscaled transform should have the FT_Size and the FT_Transform from the FT_Face applied to it and then it would already just be in the right space without needing to drag \u0027scale\u0027 into this (which seems to be the right value only when there is no skew and the size is greater than one and maybe a few other things).\n\nOf course, it would still need to be flipped when converted from FT units to SK units.",
      "revId": "85b37637cbc8e77babcc641bad511013f1b608ea",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02"
    },
